    (ingest/, guardrail/, scripts/, .github/, and any future synthesis/ code).

  * The derived VAULT CONTENT (L1 source notes, L2 weekly briefs, L3 rule
    notes — i.e. everything under vault/) is licensed separately under
    Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International (CC BY 4.0).
    See LICENSE-CONTENT.md.

